## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- No existing test suite found in the project.

### Dev Server Validation
```bash
# From d:\My Projects\my-portfolio
npm run dev
```
Navigate to `http://localhost:3000` and verify:
1. All sections visible and scroll correctly
2. PWA manifest loads (`http://localhost:3000/manifest.json`)
3. No console errors
4. Responsive on mobile viewport (Chrome DevTools)
5. Typewriter animation and skill bars animate on load

### Manual Browser Check (via browser_subagent)
- Screenshot each major section after launch
- Verify dark theme, gradients, and animations are working
- Check mobile hamburger menu toggle
